sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Super Admin
    participant CP as Control Panel
    participant API as Backend API
    participant REPO as User Repository
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>CP: 1. Pilih menu user
    CP->>API: 2. GET Request /user
    API->>REPO: 3. getAllUsers()
    REPO->>DB: 4. Query data User
    DB-->>REPO: 5. Data Users
    REPO-->>API: 5.1 Data Users
    API-->>CP: 5.2 Data Users
    CP->>Admin: 6. Menampilkan data users
    Admin->>CP: 7. Klik menu "Aksi"
    CP->>Admin: 8. Menampilkan menu-menu aksi
    Admin->>CP: 9. Klik menu "Edit"
    CP->>Admin: 10. Menampilkan form edit user
    Admin->>CP: 11. Input data user
    CP->>API: 12. PUT Request /user/{id}
    API->>API: 13. Validasi Input
    alt Username sudah ada
        API-->>CP: 13.1.1 Pesan error
        CP->>Admin: 13.1.2 Menampilkan pesan error
    else Username belum ada
        API->>REPO: 13.2.2 updateUser()
        REPO->>DB: 13.2.3 Update data User
        DB-->>REPO: 13.2.4 Data User
        REPO-->>API: 13.2.5 Data User
        API-->>CP: 13.2.6 Data User
        CP->>Admin: 13.2.7 Menampilkan pesan berhasil update user
        CP->>Admin: 13.2.8 Redirect ke halaman user
    end